              %img{:alt => "Networks", :src => "images/icons/network.gif"}/
          %li
            %a{:href => "#contact", :title => "contact"}
              %img{:alt => "Contact", :src => "images/icons/contact.gif"}/
        #content
          #scrollWrapper
            %ul
              / Home Section Details
              %li#home.section
                %h1
                  Mustafa Quilon
                  %a.vcard{:href => "myVcard.vcf", :title => "Download vCard"}
                    %img{:alt => "Download vCard", :src => "images/icons/vcard.gif"}/
                  / Link to your vcard file
                %h3 UI Designer / Front-end Web Developer / Evangelist
                / end #home
              / About Section Details
              %li#about.section
                %h2 About Me
                %img.left{:alt => "Your Name", :src => "images/avatar.jpg"}/
                %p
                  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam ultricies magna non lectus elementum consectetur. Aliquam erat volutpat. Nulla et imperdiet mauris. Etiam ac ante id arcu luctus suscipit non sed leo. Donec malesuada dapibus purus ac dictum. Vestibulum quis odio mi, et accumsan metus. Aliquam erat volutpat.
